    <item>
      <title>据《华尔街日报》报道，苹果与 Meta 就人工智能合作展开谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/apple-meta-have-held-talks-for-an-ai-partnership-wsj-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《华尔街日报》报道，Meta Platforms Inc. 已与苹果公司进行了谈判，商讨将其母公司 Facebook 的生成人工智能模型整合到这家 iPhone 制造商的人工智能系统 Apple Intelligence 中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/apple-meta-have-held-talks-for-an-ai-partnership-wsj-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 18:01:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nvidia 的销售额增长速度太快，华尔街都跟不上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/nvidia-sales-grow-so-fast-that-wall-street-can-t-keep-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Nvidia Corp. 是标准普尔 500 指数中最昂贵的股票，其股价约为该公司未来 12 个月预计销售额的 23 倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/nvidia-sales-grow-so-fast-that-wall-street-can-t-keep-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 16:00:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果计划如何将 Vision Pro 打造成一家多产品企业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-06-23/apple-vision-plans-cheaper-model-in-late-2025-vision-pro-2-in-2026-ar-glasses-lxrjk6wu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Apple Vision Pro 起步缓慢，促使管理层重新考虑该设备的计划。但该公司仍希望将这款耳机打造成一个多产品类别。此外：苹果继续其产品淘汰狂潮；最新转向 M4 Mac；以及为什么 Apple Intelligence 没有出现在大多数 iPhone 上——或欧盟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-06-23/apple-vision-plans-cheaper-model-in-late-2025-vision-pro-2-in-2026-ar-glasses-lxrjk6wu</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 12:45:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
